          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Office of Government Ethics Independence Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Ethics in Government Act of 1978 to specify that the Director of the Office of Government Ethics may be removed only pursuant to a finding by the President of neglect of duty or malfeasance in office. </p>]]></text>
